title: Authme登陆插件问题
author: yanweichen
txt_content:
Authme登陆插件提示将会关闭服务器

[14:04:13 WARN]: [AuthMe] THE SERVER IS GOING TO SHUT DOWN AS DEFINED IN THE CONFIGURATION!
[14:04:13 INFO]: [AuthMe] Waiting for 0 tasks to finish
[14:04:13 INFO]: [AuthMe] AuthMe 5.3.2-b1726 disabled!



我两个服务器在一台主机上
都是用的Authme登陆插件
另一个服务器不会这样
